snippet.textDisplay:
Clash of Clans is jumping the shark bigtime, with more and more ridiculous stuff in every town hall upgrade. Used to be TH11 lasted for at least 2 years, and now they’re coming up with new TH every year, just in time for holidays so kids can ask their parents to gem a new town hall with all the old and new stuff maxed out as a xmas present.
I guess they’re trying to rake in cash from this Clash of Clans revival this last year cos it used to be stale for a few years, same old same old raiding and upgrading for 6-7 years now.
It’s still the same stuff they’re just trying to create buzz with the promo campaign on social media and these new ridiculous upgrades.
Anyway I was just trying to keep up with the upgrades although I done a proper RAID in at least a year, just from the gold/lix from the mines/pumps.
Havent really completed the TH12 stuff yet, out comes TH13. 😭😭
I don’t think I’ll be able to keep up with it since I don’t really feel like clashing anymore since 2 years ago.
I don’t really feel excited for the upgrade. I see top players already gemmed all the new stuff, so there’s that. Kids don’t waste real money for the upgrades, it gets boring after a while, its repetitive.
